{% comment %} Accent color — decoupled from product button color (cod_primary_color). {% endcomment %}
{% comment %} Priority: 1) edited preset/custom border → 2) preset theme color → 3) fallback #111827 {% endcomment %}
{% unless cod_styles_parsed %}{% assign cod_styles_parsed = cod_styles | parse_json %}{% endunless %}
